Params: {3: 'How she was born and grew up. All the time she spent in this city in the sea.'}
{3: 'Everyone looked and laughed at her as if she was a monkey.'}
{3: 'Lamia always thinks she is too foolish for Atlantis. An unneeded presence. From then on, Lamia becomes constrained and introverted, fearing that her actions would annoy anyone.'}
{3: 'She never showed her a good face.'}
{3: 'Lamia vaguely remembers that the cold war between her and Lustrous lasted a long time, until an inevitable event took place.'}
{3: 'She still remembers that day when the entire Atlantis was shaken by the screeching alarm.'}
{3: 'It is said that a virus named "Punishing" has swept the entire world during the submergence of Atlantis.'}
